    "en": {
      "title": "National fuel license is being tested on 4708 vehicles",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister of Electricity and Energy Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said that the national fuel license system was tested on 4708 vehicles yesterday.",
        "He said that this system was supposed to be tested in 25 fuel stations yesterday, but due to the practical problems of issuing fuel, the system could be tested in only 20 fuel stations.",
        "The Minister mentions that the next two days will be checked in the remaining 05 fuel stations."
      ],
